  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1543022/" class="title-link">一本很详尽的“中国哲学概念史”</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1543022"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1288587/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1288587-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1288587/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">gd19111212</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-11-02"
      class="main-meta">2008-11-02 11:34:40</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1543022_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  由于时间限制，目前只能挑着读，不过以后有空的话，我一定会好好的再读这本书。 唯一的问题，就是作者使用的语法不太合乎现代汉语（大陆）的规范，需要读者自己调整，不过读完二十页之后也就习惯了，能坚持把这本书读完，是有大好处的！

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1543022/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1543022_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1543022_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





